{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"圣军  一九五○年八一建军节献给朱总司令","authors":["黄炎培"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":7,"day":1}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"圣军"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄炎培"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九五○年八一建军节献给朱总司令"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自有人类，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从没有发现过这样的军队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任何凶狠的敌人——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒋介石，陆海空，人员几百万，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到它的面前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粉碎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任何现代化装备——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美帝国主义，送给蒋介石，飞机、大炮、坦克，一批又一批，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到它的面前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连人带械一齐来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这算什么！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽管百战百胜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何尝觉得它可怕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只觉得它——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可爱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可敬！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一个大城市，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风雨中间站着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马路旁边躺着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连一杯白水送给它都不饮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老百姓涌上来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争先地——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢迎它，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拥抱它，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难解难分。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它和老百姓怎么还可能“分”呢！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它本身就是老百姓。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（三）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“起来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"起来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不愿做奴隶的人们！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有人民自己才能解放人民。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中华一部近世史，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清清楚楚地写着："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“五四”是有组织的群众运动第一声；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"后来经过了多少尝试，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吸取了多少经验；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“八一”是中国共产党领导着的民众开始正式地武装起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来发动革命战争。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它又饱受了高度的长期的多少艰苦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这中间那里还数得清！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫忘！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫忘！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二万五千里长征。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（四）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二万五千里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它从南方的五岭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向西绕一个大圈儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来到了陕北长城。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁都打成钢了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看一阵阵落花流水般的追兵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从此，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它深入了农村，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎样秋收？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎样春耕？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽量地吸收了切实而丰富的生活经验和政治经验，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从艰苦中间获得了饱满的生命。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"靠天吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"靠人吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自力更生！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（五）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八年抗日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它从高度的长期的艰苦中间壮大了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"左一队游击，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"右一队游击，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从黑龙江联接到了海南岛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还从逐步的“土改”中间，团结了爱国的农民不少。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扩大的武装起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"加强的组织起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒋介石藐视它了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前前后后，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少战场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一面倒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可恨又可笑；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美帝国主义毒忌它了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枉用了心机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不打自招，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请读一九四九年八月五日艾奇逊白皮书的报道。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到今朝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它在基本上已经解放了中华整个大陆的男女和老小。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朱总司令，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是正确的方针指导，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是崇高的精神感召。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（六）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那里像军队！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学习，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"操练，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"运动和游戏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"批评和检讨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一天又一天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从早起到夜眠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"简直是一群学校青年！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它生活在乐园，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它操作在农田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"替老百姓服务，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么都心甘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那知道它善于作战，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不用说了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已经取得了全世界人民的称赞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那知道它还善于团结，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"团结了自己，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还团结了复复杂杂的中华全国。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请看西北，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少兄弟民族，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民解放军到了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快快乐乐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如手如足，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无拘无束。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（七）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远光荣着的“八一”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在一九二七年的今天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是它诞生的第一个清晨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从南昌的古城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"创造了中华的新生。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这二十多年中间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说不尽它的奇迹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写不尽它的奇勋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它简直把四万万七千五百万人的大民族翻了身，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还鼓励了东方许多被压迫民族，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最近像朝鲜人民英勇地击溃了美帝侵略的军队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使得太平洋人民民主壁垒一新，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它将组合了各国人民力量，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来保卫到世界的和平，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人类的安宁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任何人对它不可能提出更多的要求了么！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽让你们提出更苛刻的批评，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只从我内心中间想给它一个题名："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“圣军”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}